<span id="cb1-17"><a href="#cb1-17" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="fu">## Три режима работы vi</span></span>
<span id="cb1-18"><a href="#cb1-18" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a></span>
<span id="cb1-19"><a href="#cb1-19" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="pp">|</span> Режим <span class="pp">|</span> Назначение <span class="pp">|</span></span>
<span id="cb1-20"><a href="#cb1-20" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="pp">|-------|------------|</span></span>
<span id="cb1-21"><a href="#cb1-21" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="pp">|</span> Командный <span class="pp">|</span> Навигация, удаление, копирование, вставка <span class="pp">|</span></span>
<span id="cb1-22"><a href="#cb1-22" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="pp">|</span> Вставки <span class="pp">|</span> Ввод и редактирование текста <span class="pp">|</span></span>
<span id="cb1-23"><a href="#cb1-23" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="pp">|</span> Последней строки <span class="pp">|</span> Сохранение, выход, поиск <span class="pp">|</span></span>
<span id="cb1-24"><a href="#cb1-24" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a></span>
